ias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Hani\u2019 reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace blessings be upon him, in the year of the liberation, and I found him taking a bath. When the Prophet finished his bath, he performed eight cycles of prayer, and that was in the forenoon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 357,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/every-morning-joints-owe\/","url_meta":{"origin":28175,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Every morning your joints owe charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cUpon every one of your joints in the morning is charity due. Every glorification of Allah is charity. Every praise of Allah is charity. Every declaration of the oneness of Allah is charity. Every exaltation of Allah is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42910,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/09\/best-salat-al-duha\/","url_meta":{"origin":28175,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Duha: Best time for forenoon prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 9, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Arqam reported: He saw some people performing the forenoon prayer, and he said, \u201cThey already know that prayer at a different time is better.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe forenoon prayer of the penitent is when young camels can feel the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/04\/salat-al-duha-four-rakaat\/","url_meta":{"origin":28175,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Four cycles of Salat al-Duha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Son of Adam, bow to Me in four cycles of prayer\u00a0at the beginning of the day and I will suffice you for the rest of it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 475 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36412,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-al-duha-tawbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28175,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Salat al-Duha is prayer of repentant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone preserve the forenoon prayer but the penitent. It is the prayer of the penitent.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 1224 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u